<div class="container">

<div id="myCarousel" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel">
    <!-- Indicators -->
    <div class="jumbotron" id="home2">
					<h1>Welcome, <span class="pull-right"> <%= link_to image_tag(current_user.avatar_url),"#", class: "img-circle" %>
					 <%=current_user.username %></span></h1>
					</div>
    <ol class="carousel-indicators">
      <li data-target="#myCarousel" data-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
      <li data-target="#myCarousel" data-slide-to="1"></li>
      <li data-target="#myCarousel" data-slide-to="2"></li>
      <li data-target="#myCarousel" data-slide-to="3"></li>
    </ol>

    <!-- Wrapper for slides -->
    <div class="carousel-inner" role="listbox">

      <div class="item active">
      <%=link_to image_tag("spring-time.jpg"), '#Home', class: "frame" %>
        <div class="carousel-caption">
          <h3>Ansel Adams</h3>
          <p>"When words become unclear, I shall focus with photographs. When images become inadequate, I shall be content with silence."</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="item">
        <%=link_to image_tag("clock.jpg"), '#Home', class: "frame" %>
        <div class="carousel-caption">
          <h3>Hselmak</h3>
          <p>"Capture the moment now or else its gone forever, just leaving behind the tained memmories with the happiness."</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    
      <div class="item">
        <%=link_to image_tag("alone.jpg"), '#Home', class: "frame" %>
        <div class="carousel-caption">
          <h3>Leonardo</h3>
          <p>"Even the silence says the thousand words, a picture can show the thousand emotions of the moments that has been lived and still feels alive somewhere."</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="item">
        <%=link_to image_tag("family.jpg"), '#Home', class: "frame" %>
        <div class="carousel-caption">
          <h3>Happiness forever.....</h3>
          <p>"Everytime you can't be happy, but the glimse of the happiness of all the time will always be right in front of you always."</p>
        </div>
      </div>
  
    </div>

    <!-- Left and right controls -->
    <a class="left carousel-control" href="#myCarousel" role="button" data-slide="prev">
      <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-left" aria-hidden="true"></span>
      <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
    </a>
    <a class="right carousel-control" href="#myCarousel" role="button" data-slide="next">
      <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-right" aria-hidden="true"></span>
      <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
    </a>
  </div>
</div>
<br>

















